headline: GE HealthCare Announces Initiative to Help Address Radiologic Technologist Shortage
summary: CHICAGO, November 12, 2024--GE HealthCare (Nasdaq: GEHC) today announced an initiative with AMN Healthcare aimed at helping address the critical shortage of radiologic technologists (rad tech) in the healthcare industry. This initiative helps healthcare providers meet their immediate staffing needs through AMN Healthcare’s comprehensive workforce solutions and GE HealthCare’s innovative technologies and training expertise.
